name: Lumpy the Gnome
description: Lumpy is just capable enough to move logs from one location to another.
autoCollectMessage: Lumpy carrys off $ logs, stumbling the entire way.

name: Dumpy the Gnome
description: Dumpy is more than capable enough to move logs from one location to another.
autoCollectMessage: Dumpy slowly carrys off $ logs.

name: Grumpy the Gnome
description: Grumpy will move logs from one location to another, but he won't be happy about it.
autoCollectMessage: Grumpy mutters to himself while he takes $ logs to the bank.

name: Slumpy the Gnome
description: Slumpy is quite quick at carrying logs. It's a shame you can't do anything about his posture.
autoCollectMessage: Slumpy drags $ logs away to the bank.

name: Rumpy the Gnome
description: Rumpy has a butt-chin which has always encouraged him to move very quickly so as to never be seen.
autoCollectMessage: Rumpy scurries off with $ logs and quickly returns, hiding behind a large boulder.

name: Jumpy the Gnome
description: Jumpy is full of energy and loves to move logs between locations.
autoCollectMessage: Jumpy maneuvers the $ logs to the bank in the most uncomfortable way.

name: Thurgood the Dwarf
description: Thurgood barely qualifies as a dwarf.
autoCollectMessage: Thurgood fills his bag with $ ores and drags it back to the bank.

name: Badthur the Dwarf
description: Badthur is probably overqualified for the job.
autoCollectMessage: Badthur fills his bag with $ ores and lugs it back to the bank.

name: Tholdbur the Dwarf
description: Tholdbur takes pride in his ability to carry ores from the mine to the bank.
autoCollectMessage: Tholdbur fills his bag with $ ores and carries it back to the bank.

name: Dwarny the Dwarf
description: Dwarny is actually a gnome. Don't tell anyone
autoCollectMessage: Dwarny fills his bag with $ ores and runs it back to the bank.

name: Skia the Monopod
description: Skia is exceptionally fast for only having one foot.
autoCollectMessage: Skia takes your finished items away and returns with more bars.

name: Tolani Seba the Scout
description: Tolani is always eager to find things.
autoCollectMessage: Tolani carries your loot away and returns to help find new prey.

name: Raka the Kushtaka
description: Raka is a very simple Kushtaka. She'll take your fish to the bank, slowly.
autoCollectMessage: Raka bags up $ fish and carries them away, slowly.

name: Al the Kushtaka
description: Al is a beginner at carrying things to the bank, but he tries his best.
autoCollectMessage: Al carries off $ fish to the bank.

name: Krim the Kushtaka
description: Krim is an average Kushtaka. Don't expect too much and you won't be disappointed.
autoCollectMessage: Krim bags up $ fish and hurries off to the bank.

name: Sloodle the Kushtaka
description: Sloodle is an exceptional helper. Her eagerness is only surpassed by her work ethic.
autoCollectMessage: Sloodle happily bags up $ fish and dutifully takes them to the bank.

name: Wenshoop the Kushtaka
description: Wenshoop is one of the greatest Kushtaka to ever live. You should feel grateful he'll even work for you, he says.
autoCollectMessage: Wenshoop haughtily bags up $ fish, and carries them off to the bank, despite being so beneath him.

name: Glindrear the Kushtaka
description: Glindrear is a master bank carry-er. He's been doing this kind of thing for years.
autoCollectMessage: Glindrear carries off $ fish, using nothing but his bare hands.

name: Grib Grab Grub Grob the Goblin
description: Perhaps the most disgusting creature you've ever seen.
autoCollectMessage: Grib Grab Grub Grob takes $ items from your bank and delivers them to the general store.

name: Anthropos en tayn Agros
description: Anthropos is a natural scout.
autoCollectMessage: Anthropos hurries off with your loot away and returns to help find something else to kill.

name: Thunkirn the Dwarf
description: Thunkirn is an excellent hauler who hasn't seen the light of day in twenty years. It's his own fault, though, with a beard like that...
autoCollectMessage: Thunkirn fills his bag with $ ores and runs it back to the bank.

name: Threnden the Dwarf
description: Threnden's wife named him so. Not that he's complaining. They used to call him Pickles. He's quite possibly the greatest mining hauler below Quepland's surface.
autoCollectMessage: Threnden fills his bag with $ ores and runs it back to the bank.

name: Pumpy the Gnome
description: Pumpy is ENERGIZED to do what you want, when you want it!
autoCollectMessage: Pumpy dashes off with $ logs to the bank and returns shortly after. He's ready for more!
